{
  "texts": [
    "A NLTK's pre-trained sentiment analyser is applied to estimate the sentiment of the sexual harassment sentence.",
    "The result provides the sentiment of positive, negative, neutral, and compound.",
    "The compound sentiment is then encoded into 'negative' where the value is less than zero, 'positive' where the value is more than zero, and 'neutral' where the value is zero.",
    "Lexicon-based emotion analysis.",
    "Text2emotion, a Python package, is used to extract the emotion of the sentences."
  ]
}